						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://literarymentoring.wordpress.com/2013/01/29/%d0%b1%d0%bb%d1%8e%d0%b7-%d0%b1%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b4%d1%8f%d1%87%d0%b5%d0%b3%d0%be-%d0%bf%d1%81%d0%b0/" rel="bookmark">Блюз бродячего пса</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="https://literarymentoring.wordpress.com/2013/01/29/%d0%b1%d0%bb%d1%8e%d0%b7-%d0%b1%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b4%d1%8f%d1%87%d0%b5%d0%b3%d0%be-%d0%bf%d1%81%d0%b0/" title="12:16 пп" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-01-29T12:16:18+00:00">29.01.2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://literarymentoring.wordpress.com/author/sergeylikhachev007/" title="Смотреть все записи автора Сергей Лихачев" rel="author">Сергей Лихачев</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
