						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://literarymentoring.wordpress.com/2013/01/28/%d1%81%d0%b0%d0%bc%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%b4%d0%b0%d1%82-%d0%b4%d1%83%d0%bc%d0%b0%d0%b9-%d0%ba%d0%b0%d0%ba-%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%b4%d0%b0%d1%82%d0%b5%d0%bb%d1%8c-4-%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b8%d0%b7%d0%b2%d0%be/" rel="bookmark"><IDXSKIP>Самиздат. Думай как издатель. 4. Производство и&nbsp;планирование</IDXSKIP></a></h1>
			
